Dumathoin is an intermediate Power of the Dwarf+pantheon. He is neutral in Alignment.
Dumathoin's portfolio includes buried wealth, earth, gems, mining, mountain dwarves, ores, secrets, and underground exploration. He is also guardian of tombs.
Dumathoin dwells in the deepest level of the Dwarven Mountain in the Outlands, called Deepshaft Hall. His realm intertwines in places with the realm of Ilsensine. 

